406
00:21:34,880 --> 00:21:36,119
Even if she’s with the underground,

407
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:37,960
I wouldn’t tell anyone.

408
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:41,440
Let me be honest with you.

409
00:21:42,359 --> 00:21:43,440
As for Chongqing,

410
00:21:43,799 --> 00:21:45,119
I lost faith in it a long time ago.

411
00:21:45,480 --> 00:21:46,519
That includes Lao Xie.

412
00:21:48,119 --> 00:21:48,920
Why?

413
00:21:49,759 --> 00:21:50,839
I think he’s changed.

414
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:53,200
He’ll turn his back on anyone to complete his mission.

415
00:21:53,599 --> 00:21:54,759
The matter at Pingjia Lane,

416
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:56,079
