422
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:06,640
He never really wanted you to leave.

423
00:22:07,039 --> 00:22:08,039
As expected.

424
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:09,839
And as of today,

425
00:22:10,960 --> 00:22:12,880
I don’t plan to leave Shanghai either.

426
00:22:13,319 --> 00:22:14,119
Why?

427
00:22:15,079 --> 00:22:16,839
Even if I die here,

428
00:22:16,839 --> 00:22:17,799
