434
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:31,480
But I don't think that way anymore

435
00:22:32,880 --> 00:22:34,759
Do you know how many of our compatriots I saw

436
00:22:35,119 --> 00:22:36,960
in No. 76

437
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:39,240
