438
00:22:40,519 --> 00:22:42,200
How many heroes I saw

439
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:43,680
sacrifice their lives?

440
00:22:45,119 --> 00:22:46,319
In times of national crisis

441
00:22:47,200 --> 00:22:48,559
