442
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:51,839
Rather than just surviving out there

443
00:22:52,119 --> 00:22:55,279
I'd rather live a passionate life here

444
00:22:56,799 --> 00:22:58,480
I will use my own way

445
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:01,240
