558
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:01,039
If it were someone else,

559
00:28:01,279 --> 00:28:02,720
they'd be half dead by now.

560
00:28:03,279 --> 00:28:05,039
Chief Hirata should know

561
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,279
I've always been lucky.

562
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:09,160
Don't say things like that.

563
00:28:09,599 --> 00:28:10,359
It's bad luck.

564
00:28:12,839 --> 00:28:14,680
I heard Miss Xie brought you here.

565
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:16,200
A beauty saving a hero,

566
00:28:16,359 --> 00:28:17,240
