573
00:28:32,000 --> 00:28:33,400
In our line of work as agents,

574
00:28:33,839 --> 00:28:35,680
we're always living on the edge.

575
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:38,400
Once we step out of headquarters,

576
00:28:38,759 --> 00:28:41,160
there are too many people who want us dead.

577
00:28:42,160 --> 00:28:44,319
